platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Meet the Heroes of Snyder's Justice League.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You can feel the love for the DC Universe coursing through this supercharged brawler. Batman, Wonder Woman, Gorilla Grodd—our favorite heroes and villains look spectacular. And the new combat system controls awesomely, letting you jump, sweep, and fling ranged attacks at Flash-like speed. Between the devastating new super-moves and cool modes (including a console-style story mode), we’re in heaven.
